  <text>
    <body>
      <head>Oppel family</head>
      <div>

        <p><ref cRef="entity-000643">Reinhard Oppel</ref> (1878–1941) was married four times, and
          had eight children.</p>

        <p>Oppel's first and third wives do not feature in his correspondence, nor do the children
          he had with them. His four wives, and the children they bore that are mentioned in the
          Oppel correspondence, were:</p>
        <lb/>

        <p>1. Catharina (Käthe) Brebeck (1884-1955), m. 1906, div. 1910</p>

        <p>2. <ref cRef="entity-006150">Gertrud Bandelow</ref> (1881-1925), m. pre-1913</p>

        <p><table rows="4" cols="2">
            <row n="1">
              <cell>– children:</cell>
              <cell/>
            </row>
            <row n="2">
              <cell/>
              <cell>1. <ref cRef="entity-000644">Ulrich</ref> (1910–)</cell>
            </row>
            <row n="3">
              <cell/>
              <cell>2. <ref cRef="entity-003957">Walter</ref> (1913–47)</cell>
            </row>
            <row n="4">
              <cell/>
              <cell>3. <ref cRef="entity-008510">Hans Reinhard</ref> (1915–90)</cell>
            </row>
          </table></p>

        <p>3. Käthe Eggeling (1892-1974), m. 1927, div. 1929</p>

        <p>4. <ref cRef="entity-005266">Elfriede Dey</ref> (1909-96), m. May 1930</p>

        <p><table rows="3" cols="2">
            <row n="1">
              <cell>– children:</cell>
              <cell/>
            </row>
            <row n="2">
              <cell/>
              <cell>1. <ref cRef="entity-008523">Kurt (Bepo)</ref> (1930–)</cell>
            </row>
            <row n="3">
              <cell/>
              <cell>2. <ref cRef="entity-008524">Brigitte</ref> (1932–)</cell>
            </row>

          </table></p>

      </div>
